## Do Not Rename

- Karen (robot vacuum) — intentional name
- PooperScooper9000 (Litter-Robot) — intentional
- Loki, Lando (cats) — intentional
- SHIELD (NVIDIA media player) — product name
- All Z-Wave technical parameter entities (alarm configs, calibration selects)
- All update.* entities — auto-managed
- All system/infrastructure entities (Zigbee2MQTT bridge, HA core, supervisor, etc.)

---

## Open Questions

1. What are the actual plant names for the 4 soil moisture sensors (Plant Sensor 1-4)?
2. Is grapheneos_pixel_7 yours? If so, rename to "Stanley Pixel 7"
3. Is light.slaapkamer_lamp a dead device to remove, or just temporarily unavailable?
4. "Lamp 3 koppen" (Shelly 1, living room) has no entities — dead device or just not integrated?
5. Are "Test" ESP32 and "FanController" ESP32 two separate physical devices, or is "Test" a replacement for the unavailable "FanController"?
6. Does "deken" (Christmas Tree Plug) serve double duty as an RGB lamp year-round, or only seasonal?
